versions.name: Google Stadia: Founder's Edition
versions.summary: Stadia Founder’s Edition lets you instantly enjoy games in up to 4K on your TV without a console. You can also play across laptops, desktops, Pixel 3, and Pixel 3a with cross-screen early access starting from day one.
